items.name: Abnormal gains / (losses)
definition: -IFNA0(fdsf!FF_IMPAIR_PPE) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_FIN_ASSETS_IMPAIR) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_XCEPT_PROV) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_REORG_RESTRUCT_EXP) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_GW_WDOWN) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_LEGAL_CLAIM_EXP) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_IMPAIR_INTANG_OTH) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_UNREAL_INVEST_GL) - fdsf!FF_OTH_UNUSUAL_EXP

items.name: Other common equity
definition: -IFNA0(fdsf!FF_COM_STK_ESOP) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_COM_EQ_FOR_EXCH) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_COM_EQ_GL) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_RSRV_REVAL) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_RSRV_APPR_OTH) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_RSRV_UNAPPR) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_TREAS_STK)

items.name: Other financing activities
definition: fdsf!FF_FIN_CF - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_DEBT_LT_ISS_CF) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_DEBT_LT_REDUCT_CF) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_DEBT_ST_CF) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_DIV_COM_CF) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_DIV_PFD_CF) - IFNA0(fdsf!FF_STK_SALE_CF) + IFNA0(fdsf!FF_STK_PURCH_CF)

items.name: Cash flows from financing
definition: IFNA0(asn!TOTAL_DEBT_ISSUED) - IFNA0(asn!TOTAL_DEBT_REPAID) - asn!DVD_PAID + IFNA0(asn!EQUITY_ISSUANCES) - IFNA0(asn!SHARE_REPO) + asn!OTHER_FINANCING_ACTIVITIES
